column2: Hello, I'm coming to see you because I have a problem, it's INFURIATING, I cannot even live that way!
<textjump=0.5|2|1>Oh no that's horrible.<textpause=1> And your favorite food is<textspeed=1>... </textjump>
Chocolate, what else ! How could someone think otherwise?!
<textjump=0.5|2|1>Obviously how could anyone think of something else... </textjump>
It's Un-ac-cep-ta-ble! Yesterday I was walking with my precious chocolate and the police arrested me! You'll never know why!?
<textjump=0.5|2|1>It's not that serious,<textspeed=5> this is just chocolate Emile. </textjump>

<playsound=wrong_choice> <textjump=0.5|2|1>What?!<b><color=red> Not<textspeed=30></textjump><textjump=0.3|-1|5> THAT</textjump><textjump=0.5|2|1><textspeed=15><textpause=0.5><b></color> serious? The chocolate? But my whole life<color=red><textspeed=30></textjump><textjump=0.3|-1|5> IS</textjump><textjump=0.5|2|1><textspeed=15><textpause=0.5><b></color> chocolate! </textjump>
<textjump=0.5|2|1>When I was a kid my plushie was a<color=#ffafc1><textspeed=10> chocolate bar</color>! </textjump>

<textjump=0.5|2|1>All my life I went to festivals where<color=red> Chococo</color>, the most cocoa-like mascot were and every time he offered me <color=red><b><camerashake=1|0.5><textspeed=20>CHOCOLATE</color>! </textjump>
Do you know what my wife was covered in on the most magical evening of my life ?
Think about the chocolate you love and focus on my watch...
Think about the candy you love and focus on my watch...
<playsound=wrong_choice> <textspeed=40><textjump=0.2|2|10>Who do you take me for? I'm not a<textrumble=0.1|-1|2><color=red><camerashake=1|0.2> KID</color></textrumble>!!
Now think about somebody you love, who relaxes you.
<playsound=wrong_choice> <textspeed=40><textjump=0.2|2|10>I<color=red><textrumble=0.1|-1|2> hate</textrumble><textjump=0.2|2|10></color> my parents<textspeed=30> I don't want to talk about it!
No, to appease me talk about the cocoa-like mascot, say his name.

<textjump=0.5|2|1>Your<color=#6500c5><textjump=0.5|-1|5> eyelids</color></textjump><textjump=0.5|2|1> are<color=#6500c5><textjump=0.5|-1|5> heavy</color></textjump><textjump=0.5|2|1>, you seem to<color=#6500c5><textjump=0.5|-1|5> fall</color></textjump><textjump=0.5|2|1> and let go of all your<color=#6500c5><textjump=0.5|-1|5> problems</textjump><textjump=0.5|2|1></color><textspeed=1>......
<textjump=0.5|2|1>Make him fight anything in his way for his precious chocolate!
<textjump=0.5|2|1>Chocolate is nothing to you anymore! You forget about it and live your life avoiding it!
Chocolate is too important for you! And you will fight ANYTHING that goes in your way to still appreciate it!
